text: Jerry Phele (born 1 July 1956) is a South African Sotho born actor who is most known for acting on Emzini Wezinsizwa as Mofokeng. He has also starred on other notable TV series such as Skwizas and The Throne. ==References== ==External Links== Category:Living people Category:1956 births Category:South African male actors
